version_description:
Thank you for always using SMPro. We added iPhoneX frame.
However, in order to continue development in the future, we set up additional charge for saving iPhoneX.
"Saving iPhoneX" a separate charge independent of "Unlimited Save".
Thank you!

· Add iPhoneX Frames
· Fix iPhone 7 Left frame
· Move development language to Swift
· Fixed bug there was in version 2.2
